Selection was performed based on the following inclusion criteria: (1) prospective study, including randomized and nonrandomized clinical trials and open trials;

Exclusion criteria consisted of (1) duplicate publication; (2) retrospective or observational study;

Therefore, we excluded retrospective studies to minimize unidentified biases and assumed that the degree of repigmentation after a given protocol would represent the efficacy of phototherapy in prospective studies.
